. 玩支那佬見口罩值錢，就一窩蜂咁走去造，而家街外好撚多呢d垃圾，少不免都係唔好亂買，如果買唔到大牌子，我會買香港製口罩.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd58b2995522b1b6426ad7e6a37f4dd7d3ae07c","tid":1950163,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5c7d7993289b8cc7ea621bc230f1657f083141e","tid":1950163,"uid":44171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:06:08.000Z","msg":"醫管局都開始用支那口罩，但有人講又爛有垃圾連蟲都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:18:35.000Z","msg":"支那山寨廠買唔到原材料，就用廢料加工重用，但又冇做足消毒，好似過年時救救口罩咁，所以真係有蟲都唔奇，我過年前兩日喺藥房都買咗盒救救，未到過年已經扔晒！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://kireikami.com/kyukyumask/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkireikami.com%2Fkyukyumask%2F&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2f7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=b03d6532\" target=\"_blank\">https://kireikami.com/kyukyumask/</a>"}]}